            <section>
                <label>Project Summary (100–150 words)</label>
                <p class="answer">GreenBridge Composites will design, prototype, and field‑test modular bridge‑deck panels made from plant‑based bio‑resins reinforced with recycled carbon fibre. The project aims to demonstrate a 40&nbsp;% weight reduction and 25&nbsp;% life‑cycle emission cut versus conventional steel‑reinforced concrete decks, while matching or exceeding CSA‑S6‑19 structural performance standards.</p>
            </section>

